<p>本目录收录东北萨满教相关神话人物与神明，包括满族、鄂伦春族、鄂温克族、赫哲族等北方民族的萨满教神祇。</p>
<h3 id="主要神祇">主要神祇</h3>
<ul>
<li>阿布卡赫赫：天神、创世女神</li>
<li>巴纳吉额姆：萨满女神</li>
<li>玛鲁神：家族保护神</li>
<li>吉雅奇：火神</li>
<li>尼桑萨满：传奇女萨满</li>
<li>多龙格格：雷神</li>
<li>木克嘎利：水神</li>
<li>敖包：祭坛神</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="目录结构">目录结构</h3>
<ul>
<li>东北萨满教总述.md</li>
<li>东北萨满教人物关系考.md</li>
<li>各神明专文</li>
</ul>]]></description></item><item><title>中国西南神话</title><link>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/southwest-chinese/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>老梵</author><guid>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/southwest-chinese/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h2 id="中国西南神话">中国西南神话</h2>
<p>本目录收录中国西南地区彝族、苗族、傣族、白族、纳西族、藏族等民族的神话人物与神明，涵盖创世神、英雄神、本主神、祖先神等。</p>
<h3 id="主要神祇">主要神祇</h3>
<ul>
<li>支格阿鲁：彝族创世英雄</li>
<li>帕雅拉武：傣族创世神</li>
<li>丁巴什罗：纳西族东巴教祖师</li>
<li>格萨尔王：藏族史诗英雄</li>
<li>盘瓠：苗族始祖神</li>
<li>本主：白族保护神</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="目录结构">目录结构</h3>
<ul>
<li>中国西南神话总述.md</li>
<li>中国西南神话人物关系考.md</li>
<li>各神明专文</li>
</ul>]]></description></item><item><title>江南神话</title><link>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/jiangnan-mythology/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>老梵</author><guid>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/jiangnan-mythology/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h2 id="江南神话">江南神话</h2>
<p>本目录收录中国江南地区（江苏、浙江、上海、安徽、江西部分区域）的神话与民间传说，涵盖吴越神话、江南水神、白蛇传、梁祝传说、济公传说等。</p>
<h3 id="主要神祇与传说">主要神祇与传说</h3>
<ul>
<li>白素贞：白蛇传主角，修炼千年的白蛇精</li>
<li>梁山伯与祝英台：爱情悲剧，化蝶传说</li>
<li>济公：活佛济公，疯癫僧人，济世救人</li>
<li>吴王阖闾：吴国开国君主，吴越文化代表</li>
<li>西施：春秋美女，投身太湖的传说</li>
<li>范蠡：助越王勾践复国，后成商圣</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="目录结构">目录结构</h3>
<ul>
<li>江南神话总述.md</li>
<li>江南神话人物关系考.md</li>
<li>各传说专文</li>
</ul>]]></description></item><item><title>希腊神话</title><link>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/greek/</link><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 11:37:00 +0800</pubDate><author>老梵</author><guid>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/greek/</guid><description></description></item><item><title>中国神话</title><link>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/chinese/</link><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 08:46:00 +0800</pubDate><author>老梵</author><guid>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/chinese/</guid><description></description></item><item><title>美索不达米亚神话</title><link>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/mesopotamian/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 21:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>老梵</author><guid>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/mesopotamian/</guid><description></description></item><item><title>印度神话</title><link>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/india/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 21:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>老梵</author><guid>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/india/</guid><description></description></item><item><title>波斯神话</title><link>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/persian/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>老梵</author><guid>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/persian/</guid><description></description></item><item><title>东南亚神话</title><link>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D/southeast-asia/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>老梵</author><guid>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-bl